Dialogue: 5,0:01:59.39,0:02:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm the only one who lives in this place.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:18.09,0:02:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...
Dialogue: 5,0:02:20.04,0:02:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}there's something else here that I can't see.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:28.62,0:02:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you... for the food.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:32.14,0:02:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After all this time, I don't find it that scary anymore.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:38.80,0:02:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It must be some sort of deity or god, I think.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:47.70,0:02:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In this place, it's always nighttime.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.11,0:03:01.12,Mushisode Title,,0,0,0,eptitle,{\fad(2000,0)\an7\bord0\blur0.6\p1\c&HAC94A9&\pos(-2,66)\fscx600\fscy90}m 0 0 l 100 0 100 100 0 100
Dialogue: 2,0:02:55.11,0:03:01.12,Mushisode Title,,0,0,0,eptitle,{\fad(2000,0)\an4\blur0.6\pos(30,108)}A Sea of Otherworldly Stars
Dialogue: 5,0:03:15.69,0:03:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:17.17,0:03:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,My doll is gone.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:19.91,0:03:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It must have hidden it again.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:31.59,0:03:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:34.14,0:03:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I won again today!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:47.26,0:03:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:05.40,0:04:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder what lies beyond that sky.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:15.09,0:04:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe everyone went someplace beyond the sky,
Dialogue: 5,0:04:18.38,0:04:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and that's the reason there's nobody here now.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:42.15,0:04:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This all seems so familiar.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:43.88,0:04:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I feel like I've seen a tiny starry sky like that before.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:02.15,0:05:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But in this place,
Dialogue: 5,0:05:08.09,0:05:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}everything is just so beautiful and so comfortable.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:15.90,0:05:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Compared to {that}it, even remembering \Nmy past seems like nothing but a chore.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:35.27,0:05:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:38.42,0:05:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:41.09,0:05:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Izumi here?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:44.68,0:05:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who's he?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:47.62,0:05:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming in.{Pardon the intrusion.}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:52.48,0:05:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:54.00,0:05:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone here?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:57.97,0:05:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, what a huge house.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:00.95,0:06:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:03.26,0:06:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems I'm out of time already.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:07.39,0:06:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:08.93,0:06:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,600)}I'd better increase the dosage next time...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:17.98,0:06:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Where could he have gone?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:32.91,0:06:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:35.66,0:06:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Found you.{like moths to the flame.}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:44.48,0:06:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mizuho.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:45.69,0:06:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:49.21,0:06:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Playing with Izumi.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:52.15,0:06:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Not you too. Enough already.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:55.45,0:06:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop that nonsense.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:57.05,0:07:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother's asked over \Nanother one of those strange people, too.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:02.60,0:07:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:03.82,0:07:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumi was kidnapped, by a real person.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:07.41,0:07:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise I'll find whoever did it,
Dialogue: 5,0:07:09.53,0:07:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,so cut all this out already.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:13.41,0:07:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:15.79,0:07:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I really did see her.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:19.60,0:07:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You just dreamed that up!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:22.37,0:07:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There was nothing at the bottom of that well.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:48.92,0:07:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ginko?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:50.84,0:07:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:51.90,0:07:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:54.25,0:07:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,How did it go?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:55.55,0:07:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you find Izumi?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:56.61,0:07:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I unfortunately ran out of time.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:00.81,0:08:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:04.34,0:08:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can say for sure \Nthat your daughter is alive and in this house.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:10.70,0:08:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You're simply unable to perceive each other right now.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:16.32,0:08:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,However, one must exercise caution \Nwhen synchronizing with the other side.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:22.01,0:08:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone were to stay there too long,
Dialogue: 5,0:08:24.17,0:08:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,they might forget to return as well...{"as well" is intentionally vague here in my edit. It could be "just like Izumi forgot" or "forget to return just like forgetting other memories."}
Dialogue: 5,0:08:27.89,0:08:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,especially if they're {someone }attuned to that side.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:34.52,0:08:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I will try again first thing tomorrow.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:52.00,0:08:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumi's...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:55.04,0:08:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,here after all, isn't she?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:58.96,0:09:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You may not be able to see her, but she is.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:05.11,0:09:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:07.68,0:09:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see her?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:10.25,0:09:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:12.10,0:09:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But someone always takes my doll.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:17.02,0:09:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumi was always doing that,
Dialogue: 5,0:09:19.88,0:09:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,even though she had one of her own.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:23.55,0:09:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So even now, I play with her by hiding my doll.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:47.22,0:09:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gone again...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:51.15,0:09:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Where could it be today?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:58.84,0:10:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:00.74,0:10:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Found you.{creepy}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:05.35,0:10:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:06.39,0:10:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hear me out.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:08.53,0:10:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother asked me to bring you back home.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:12.98,0:10:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You fell into an old well in the woods {out back behind}near your home,
Dialogue: 5,0:10:16.22,0:10:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's how you came to this side.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:24.01,0:10:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:25.80,0:10:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What well?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:27.80,0:10:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This{\i0} is my home!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:31.31,0:10:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,As I suspected, you're definitely attuned to this side.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:37.23,0:10:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 5,0:10:38.88,0:10:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the place you belong is the place \Nwhere people are waiting for you.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:45.02,0:10:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond that sky over there, \Nthere are people waiting for you.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:51.12,0:10:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mom, who makes you food every day...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:54.89,0:10:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Your big sister, who hides that doll and plays with you...{Timing: Generous lead-out, please}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:59.40,0:11:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to remember.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:01.37,0:11:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't where you're supposed to be.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:08.98,0:11:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Not good.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:09.80,0:11:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm running out of time.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:12.55,0:11:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have to take matters into my own hands.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:42.33,0:11:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you do—
Dialogue: 5,0:11:43.28,0:11:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:49.67,0:11:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,300)}Izumi!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:52.85,0:11:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:56.81,0:11:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,150)}Izumi?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:59.39,0:12:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Come back!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:04.80,0:12:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Izumi!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:13.37,0:12:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mizuho.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:17.05,0:12:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There are stars shining at the bottom of the well.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:20.41,0:12:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:22.10,0:12:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:24.40,0:12:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Right there.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:25.60,0:12:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There are so many of them!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:30.17,0:12:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing there...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:32.36,0:12:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, we should go home.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:35.77,0:12:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll get in trouble if we play here.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:39.12,0:12:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:42.26,0:12:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm going to leave you behind.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:44.98,0:12:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:46.38,0:12:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait for me!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:03.44,0:13:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumi, let's play with my doll.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:07.90,0:13:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:11.58,0:13:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? There aren't as many stars this time.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:17.88,0:13:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, I'll let you borrow it.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:22.15,0:13:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No thanks.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:23.30,0:13:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll just take it back right after anyway.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:27.70,0:13:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll {\i1}give{\i0} you it, then!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:31.36,0:13:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You will?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:32.33,0:13:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:33.35,0:13:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:51.72,0:13:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, can you see them?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:53.26,0:13:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:01.87,0:14:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But there are even fewer of them now.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:07.68,0:14:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumi, are you out here?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:44.45,0:14:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing down there.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:47.48,0:14:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all I found.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:51.18,0:14:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That can't be right.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:52.91,0:14:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw Izumi fall in there.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:55.83,0:14:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:59.04,0:15:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Mizuho, you had another fight with Izumi, didn't you?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:04.75,0:15:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why she ran away.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:08.00,0:15:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumi's out there somewhere!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:26.37,0:15:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to be okay, Mom.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:28.38,0:15:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe in Mr. Ginko.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:33.87,0:15:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:04.19,0:16:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If you see smoke rising up from the well,
Dialogue: 5,0:16:06.24,0:16:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,call down to the bottom of the well.{Repetition, but it makes things clear, so I'm leaving it.}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:10.59,0:16:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. There's still some left.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:21.27,0:16:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This should be enough.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:24.24,0:16:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try to synchronize with Izumi{-san} one more time.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:29.20,0:16:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's likely that she's lost her memories,
Dialogue: 5,0:16:32.25,0:16:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,but if she can remember you, she can come back.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:35.91,0:16:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,However, my time will be limited.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:40.41,0:16:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So if I think I'm running out of time,
Dialogue: 5,0:16:42.12,0:16:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll force a link from the other side to here.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:46.68,0:16:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I've made the necessary preparations.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:49.95,0:16:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The link will allow Izumi \Nto hear your voices from this side.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:58.33,0:16:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Izumi!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:00.29,0:17:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Izumi!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:01.08,0:17:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Izumi!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:03.53,0:17:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Izumi!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:04.56,0:17:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Izumi!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:05.83,0:17:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Izumi!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:10.03,0:17:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mizuho...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:12.20,0:17:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:16.89,0:17:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,400)}I'm here!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:22.44,0:17:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)}I'm here!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:27.80,0:17:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That was Izumi's voice just now!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:30.40,0:17:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,She said, "I'm here."
Dialogue: 5,0:17:32.26,0:17:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It came from inside the house!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:38.42,0:17:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the heck is making a bonfire?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:49.07,0:17:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumi!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:53.94,0:17:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumi!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:55.15,0:17:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumi, it's you!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:10.59,0:18:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:20.16,0:18:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems the stars have come back, too.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:24.83,0:18:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But there aren't as many as before.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:31.09,0:18:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:34.22,0:18:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They're called Isei, or "Well Star" mushi.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:37.05,0:18:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,On rare occasions,
Dialogue: 5,0:18:38.29,0:18:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}they appear in wells that are near \Nan abundant flow of vital energy, known as a River of Light.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:45.52,0:18:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Well, I guess one may even liken them to \Nsparks thrown off by the River of Light itself.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:52.19,0:18:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who are exposed to lots of them \Noften go through what you went through.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:58.85,0:19:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason there are fewer of them \Nmay be that the River of Light is meandering.{Keep this comment: As a verb, "to meander" basically means "to wander, usually aimlessly." However, as a river's "meander" has a different meaning (one applicable here as well), I chose the word for its dual application in this line.}
Dialogue: 5,0:19:06.78,0:19:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:10.46,0:19:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But either way,
Dialogue: 5,0:19:12.25,0:19:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,these matters concern \Na world far removed from your own.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:17.40,0:19:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You should bid them farewell.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:24.24,0:19:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumi!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:28.17,0:19:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Come now, step aside.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:33.06,0:19:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad,
Dialogue: 5,0:19:34.26,0:19:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't come here anymore, I promise.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:39.62,0:19:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make me worry more than I already have.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:49.68,0:19:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, what's that for?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:53.64,0:19:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so the god of the well will still be able to breathe.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:26.61,0:20:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the depths of the earth,
Dialogue: 5,0:20:29.48,0:20:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}is it cold?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:31.94,0:20:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it painful?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:34.35,0:20:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it frightening?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:36.60,0:20:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it lonely?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:43.02,0:20:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Be that as it may...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:53.87,0:20:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}residing in those very depths
Dialogue: 5,0:20:56.81,0:20:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}are pure water
Dialogue: 5,0:20:59.95,0:21:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fad(0,200)}and a myriad of stars.{Timing: Generous lead-out, please}
